  "id": "database-next-js-openai-doc-search-starter",
  "kind": "integration",
  "category": "database",
  "label": "Next.js OpenAI Doc Search Starter",
  "description": "Template for building your own custom ChatGPT style doc search powered by Next.js, OpenAI, and Supabase.",
  "summary": "Use this dossier when a site needs semantic documentation search or a chat-style Q&A assistant over its own content. It provides the Supabase/OpenAI indexing pipeline, the search API route, and the implementation rules for storing embeddings in Postgres and answering only from retrieved context.",
